data.name: Bellossom_0
data.value: Man, You might be shocked by our kind's secret but...

data.name: Bellossom_1
data.value: We, ACTUALLY, do not have legs!

data.name: Answer_1
data.value: WHAT!?

data.name: Answer_2
data.value: I see...

data.name: Answer_3
data.value: That's... unsettling...

data.name: Bellossom_2
data.value: That's right. The leaves under our beany body are substitutes for legs.

data.name: Bellossom_3
data.value: Don't just worry, We'll be fine! We dance without legs, No problem!

data.name: Wigglytuff_0
data.value: What a mess... The castle is dead now...!

data.name: Wigglytuff_1
data.value: Hm? Destroyed? I apologize for not wording correctly.

data.name: Kecleon_0
data.value: Well, That settles things up!

data.name: Gapori_0
data.value: Hey, You guys saved me too! I'll give you that.

data.name: Kecleon_1
data.value: I'm sorry that I have failed to beat those guys correctly.

data.name: Gapori_1
data.value: It's fine! At least you tried your best.

data.name: Misdreavus_0
data.value: Huff... Huff!

data.name: Kecleon_2
data.value: You guys' here too?

data.name: Misdreavus_1
data.value: Did you really forgot about us!?

data.name: Kecleon_3
data.value: Oh! I'm so sorry! I didn't check the other cells!

data.name: Zigzagoon_0
data.value: Anyways, Where's the Slowking?

data.name: Gapori_2
data.value: I lament to let you know folks yet I saw Nidoqueen butchered Slowking and took its crown before that.

data.name: Gapori_3
data.value: She dumped its body into the wall out of nowhere, adding insult to injury! I call that "noclipping."

data.name: Zigzagoon_1
data.value: Damn it! We're too late!

data.name: Misdreavus_2
data.value: We'll be on time for next quest, Let's go, Zig!

data.name: Kecleon_4
data.value: Oh! I found this in the castle and forgot to give it to you. I guess it wasn't needed because Slowking died.

data.name: Kecleon_5
data.value: Anyways, I'm off now! I got a shop to run somewhere!

data.name: Gapori_4
data.value: Haaaa...

data.name: Gapori_5
data.value: *cough* W-Wait up...!

data.name: Gapori_6
data.value: Actually, I think I'll be going with you.

data.name: Gapori_7
data.value: I can't go on the quest alone, I had been defeated alone a lot on my way out.

data.name: Gapori_8
data.value: *cough*...! Give me something to recover.

data.name: Message_0
data.value: {0} handed over an Oran Berry to Gapori and ate it.

data.name: Gapori_9
data.value: Thanks, I'm feeling better now!

data.name: Gapori_10
data.value: While I am finding my way out, I should help you out as well!

data.name: Gapori_11
data.value: I'll guide you to your end since we both know about "Throwback Disaster" incident.

data.name: Gapori_12
data.value: My moves can help you on your way through the difficult dungeons.

data.name: Gapori_13
data.value: So when you have troubled getting there, Assign me in your team! So, What're you waiting for?

data.name: Gapori_14
data.value: Let's try!

data.name: Mantine_0
data.value: Remind me that I'd unpleasantly prefer play Puzznic than invest energy contending with my significant other.

data.name: Scyther_0
data.value: WHEN WILL YOU LEARN!? THAT YOUR ACTION HAS CONSEQUENCES!!

data.name: Gapori_15
data.value: Oh? Turnips? For Me?

data.name: Gapori_16
data.value: *munch munch*

data.name: Gapori_17
data.value: Thank you very much for the food! It was really appreciated!

data.name: Wigglytuff_2
data.value: That Hatenna is such a really cool gal, I like her!

data.name: Cim_0
data.value: Let's see here... The castle, once a beautiful small castle, was destroyed.

data.name: Cim_1
data.value: I can see some crumbling floors, collapsed walls, and more. Don't worry about losing hope.

data.name: Cim_2
data.value: There will be someone who will be rebuilding the whole castle, and you know who it will be.

data.name: Cim_3
data.value: and that was me! You may call me Cim!

data.name: Cim_4
data.value: I have proven my skills in carpentry and engineering. Airships, Structures-

data.name: Gapori_18
data.value: Enough of that, {0} asked whether you could also repair the bridge.

data.name: Cim_5
data.value: Um, I'd like to but me think me had decided to frankly rebuild the whole castle first.

data.name: Gapori_19
data.value: Well, That's a shame. Who's gonna fix the bridge?

data.name: Cim_6
data.value: I heard my comrades volunteered for them, but there is really no sign of them...

data.name: Cim_7
data.value: Well, just leave it to me, you can't doubt the great mighty one! I'll have those finished without a doubt, but that'll take a looooong time!

data.name: Gapori_20
data.value: A trapdoor!?

data.name: Braixen_0
data.value: Cura... Firaga... Thunda- Wait...!

data.name: Braixen_1
data.value: What kind of baloney spell name is that?

data.name: Braixen_2
data.value: Couldn't they come up with something better?
